edu.uwa.aidan.robot.world
Class RangeSensor

java.lang.Object
  edu.uwa.aidan.robot.world.RangeSensor

public class RangeSensor
extends java.lang.Object

A RangeSensor is a simple sensor that measures distance from the Robots current position to the nearest Obstacle. A RangeSensor is a simple, straight-line distance measuring sensor. A RangeSensor is blocked by Obstacles, and therefore the distance returned is the nearest Obstacle encountered by tracing a straight line from the Robots current position for a distance of SENSOR_RANGE.

Author:
Aidan Morgan
